          <h2><u>Naruto</u></h2>
          <p><q>Naruto is the main character of the Naruto series created by Masashi Kishimoto. He is a young ninja with a dream of becoming the strongest ninja and the leader of his village, the Hokage. Naruto is known for his mischievous and energetic personality, as well as his strong sense of loyalty and determination. He has a troubled past but grows into a powerful and respected ninja through hard work and perseverance.</q></p>
        </div>

