            <h2><u>Luffy</u></h2>
            <p><q> Monkey D. Luffy is the protagonist of the One Piece series created by Eiichiro Oda. He is a young pirate with the ability to stretch his body like rubber after eating a Devil Fruit. Luffy's dream is to find the legendary One Piece treasure and become the Pirate King. He is known for his carefree and optimistic nature, as well as his unwavering determination to achieve his goals.</q></p>

