            <h2><u>Sailor Moon</u></h2>
            <p><q>Sailor Moon, also known as Usagi Tsukino, is the main protagonist of the Sailor Moon series created by Naoko Takeuchi. She is a teenage girl who discovers she is the reincarnation of the legendary Sailor Guardian, Sailor Moon. Usagi is kind-hearted and clumsy but possesses strong leadership qualities and a deep sense of justice. As Sailor Moon, she fights against evil forces to protect the Earth and the galaxy, alongside her fellow Sailor Guardians. Sailor Moon is known for her iconic outfit, tiara, and magical powers, and the series is praised for its themes of friendship, love, and self-empowerment.</q></p>

